{
  "texts": [
    "At present, the number of hearing-impaired people in China is close to 30 million, which is the largest number of disabled groups in China.",
    "Sign language is the main modus of communication for the hearing impaired.",
    "Barrier-free communication is a significant way for the majority of hearing-impaired people to break the island of limited information and carry out equal social communication.",
    "The main requirement for realizing barrier-free communication for the hearing-impaired is that the hearing person can understand the sign language expression of the hearing-impaired person.",
    "It is against this background that more and more scientists and scholars have begun to pay attention to Chinese Sign Language and study it and its various recognition technologies."
  ]
}